H-VeryHigh,A-Abnormal)\nMexe;\nAUTO\nDr.M.Sowmiya\nConsultant Microbiologist\nVerified by\nQodas rotui_Goeongivg GLqvL Faium_60ie\n044-4141 2222\nNeuberg Ehrlich Laboratory Private Limited,\ninfoaneubergdlagnostics com\nNo 7, Rajiv Gandhi Salai; Industrial Estate, Perungudi; Chennai\n600096\nwwWneubergdlagnosticscom",
